The paper discusses the application of Computer Vision and Artificial Intelligence in a health-related setting, specifically in the detection of malaria using deep learning models. This suggests that the paper is likely to belong to the Computer Vision (cs.CV) and Artificial Intelligence (cs.AI) sub-categories. The paper also discusses the issue of trust in AI systems, which could fall under the sub-categories of Machine Learning (cs.LG), Human-Computer Interaction (cs.HC), and Cybersecurity (cs.CY).
